<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/708097-ok-so-i-have-to-do-an-literary-critical">OK so i have to do an literary critical analysis essay on A Blaze of Glory. The essay has to be 5-8 pages not including title page, notes, or bibliography. We have to use a minimum of 3 book sources. I do not know where &amp; how to start except i have bought &amp; read the whole series by Shaara. What kind of books do i need? I need help ASAP my paper is due on may 20.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_708097'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F12788665-a-blaze-of-glory">like</a></span>

