<div id="review_3373863037" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3373863037" />
    <a title="Amgad Agaiby" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19579953-amgad-agaiby"><img alt="Amgad Agaiby" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1589541313p2/19579953.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3373863037?book_show_action=true">Jun 06, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amgad Agaiby" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amgad Agaiby" href="/user/show/19579953-amgad-agaiby">Amgad Agaiby</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer3373863037&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3373863037" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14311557633256583210">Vivid description of one of the bloodiest and most pivotal battles of the American civil war. I liked the panoramic way of telling the story and the deep prospective of the human agony. It is too lengthy though and I guess it requires great deal of concentration and mental effort to avoid being lost in the maze of details.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


