<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15981669-a-chain-of-thunder"><img alt="A Chain of Thunder (Civil War: 1861-1865, Western Theater, #2)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1360096615l/15981669._SY75_.jpg" />
