<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18373208-the-smoke-at-dawn"><img alt="The Smoke at Dawn (Civil War: 1861-1865, Western Theater, #3)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1395611383l/18373208._SY75_.jpg" />
